WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
ظآزPut every twist behind youظآز

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
ظآزDrift leisurely through timeظآز

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
ظآزMake headway against the windظآز

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
ظآزLet mountains bow to your paceظآز

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.344 --> 01:37.744
=Episode 16=

02:01.890 --> 02:03.131
Above us all,

02:04.330 --> 02:05.491
heaven exists.

02:08.571 --> 02:12.450
May Grandmother rest in peace
and go to heaven.

02:26.928 --> 02:33.210
(Ye Mansion)

02:33.210 --> 02:36.291
Li! Wait a moment, Li.

02:38.610 --> 02:39.971
You may get on the carriage first.

02:47.770 --> 02:49.050
Just get to the point.

02:50.730 --> 02:53.811
I want to know why you didn't expose me.

02:55.490 --> 02:56.890
That's because you helped me too.

02:57.930 --> 02:59.691
You helped me scare Father.

02:59.930 --> 03:01.330
I helped you hide your secret.

03:01.811 --> 03:03.890
We helped each other, so we're even.

03:04.930 --> 03:06.091
Don't you hate me?

03:07.490 --> 03:08.490
For what?

03:09.251 --> 03:11.371
For trying to steal my dowry

03:12.050 --> 03:13.571
and my mother's shop?

03:14.811 --> 03:17.490
But I already took all of those back.

03:18.050 --> 03:21.968
And I also made you lose face in public.

03:27.291 --> 03:28.890
I married your father,

03:29.691 --> 03:30.971
which caused your mother...

03:31.490 --> 03:33.170
That matter has nothing to do with you.

03:34.131 --> 03:35.490
Even without you back then,

03:36.450 --> 03:38.691
they would still have driven my mom out.

03:39.490 --> 03:42.050
If Father hadn't married you,
he would have married someone else.

03:42.610 --> 03:46.650
If I should hate anyone,
it should be him, not you.

03:49.330 --> 03:51.531
Ye Wenhua is heartless, faithless,

03:51.971 --> 03:53.050
cowardly, and incompetent.

03:53.971 --> 03:55.971
He is not a good man for any woman.

03:56.251 --> 03:59.091
Marrying him might not
be a good thing for you.

03:59.691 --> 04:01.930
How you live your life
is your own business.

04:01.930 --> 04:03.490
I shouldn't interfere too much.

04:03.930 --> 04:05.490
But Ye Rong is a good child.

04:06.411 --> 04:07.691
Be a responsible mother.

04:10.371 --> 04:12.691
And Ye Ying

04:13.571 --> 04:15.371
needs your care as well.

04:16.530 --> 04:18.090
I hope that before you act,

04:18.811 --> 04:20.731
you remember to think more about them.

04:22.131 --> 04:23.051
I will.

04:24.811 --> 04:25.611
Thank you.

04:28.571 --> 04:30.290
I'm leaving now. Take care.

04:32.371 --> 04:33.171
Li.

04:35.770 --> 04:37.090
Will you ever come back?

04:40.240 --> 04:42.768
(Ye Mansion)

05:17.648 --> 05:19.856
(Ye Mansion)

06:43.410 --> 06:44.210
Li.

06:46.210 --> 06:47.171
What are you doing?

06:49.731 --> 06:50.691
I'm hungry.

06:57.571 --> 06:59.770
You said you were hungry, right? Eat up.

07:00.731 --> 07:01.770
You can actually cook?

07:02.251 --> 07:04.210
It's just a simple meal.

07:07.491 --> 07:09.330
If you're hungry, just let Ding cook.

07:09.691 --> 07:11.650
No matter how late it is,
he can cook for you.

07:12.131 --> 07:13.330
Stop eating only sugar.

07:13.931 --> 07:15.131
I love sugar.

07:15.770 --> 07:18.090
But on Lishan Mountain,
there was no sugar.

07:18.811 --> 07:19.970
Isn't there honey to eat?

07:21.530 --> 07:22.650
It's just not the same.

07:23.251 --> 07:24.330
After there was no sugar,

07:24.731 --> 07:26.731
year after year,
I missed it more and more.

07:27.410 --> 07:28.650
Back then, I thought I wouldn't

07:28.731 --> 07:30.491
eat meals anymore
after leaving the mountain.

07:30.491 --> 07:32.571
For my three meals a day,
I'll just eat sugar.

07:43.251 --> 07:44.011
Alright, enough.

07:44.011 --> 07:44.850
Stop adding more.

07:50.210 --> 07:51.011
Li.

07:53.290 --> 07:54.251
Are you alright?

07:57.850 --> 07:58.650
I mean,

07:59.770 --> 08:03.450
since returning from Ye Mansion,
have you been alright?

08:06.571 --> 08:09.251
Of course, I am perfectly fine.

08:16.290 --> 08:17.770
Can this still taste good?

08:19.171 --> 08:21.450
It's delicious. Try it.

08:30.410 --> 08:31.210
It's good, right?

08:41.491 --> 08:42.451
I'm so full.

08:45.131 --> 08:46.251
Can you still fall asleep?

08:46.770 --> 08:47.570
Yes.

08:48.491 --> 08:51.091
Some people like to take a walk
when they overeat.

08:51.131 --> 08:53.650
Some people like to just sleep it off.

08:54.050 --> 08:56.451
My grandfather said this is a food coma,

08:56.570 --> 08:59.371
just like when people drink too much
and want to sleep.

09:01.211 --> 09:02.011
Stop.

09:04.050 --> 09:05.091
Close your eyes.

09:16.570 --> 09:17.371
Open your eyes.

09:20.971 --> 09:22.890
Qingyu brought this from Ye Mansion.

09:23.211 --> 09:24.731
I know it's something you treasured.

09:25.731 --> 09:28.368
It was broken,
so I had a craftsman fix it.

09:38.672 --> 09:42.768
ظآزThe moonlight had scattered some dustظآز

09:45.072 --> 09:49.872
ظآزAnd the cracks in memory were coveredظآز

09:52.432 --> 09:56.304
ظآزWhen did something chip away insideظآز

09:57.200 --> 10:03.568
ظآزIt's flickering,
as if expectations were lostظآز

10:06.064 --> 10:10.224
ظآزYou always love with painظآز

10:11.696 --> 10:17.168
ظآزForgetting you deserve to be loved tooظآز

10:23.371 --> 10:24.170
Qingshuang.

10:27.251 --> 10:28.131
My Lady.

10:31.824 --> 10:35.088
ظآزYou don't need to chaseظآز

10:35.312 --> 10:38.480
ظآزAfter clouds that winds pursueظآز

10:38.736 --> 10:41.872
ظآزYou can silently watch each sunriseظآز

10:42.224 --> 10:45.264
ظآزFinding happiness by your sideظآز

10:45.616 --> 10:48.784
ظآزYou don't need to chart a mapظآز

10:49.072 --> 10:52.272
ظآزOf every bend where love winds onظآز

10:52.272 --> 10:55.728
ظآزNor travel far to guide its courseظآز

10:55.728 --> 10:57.552
ظآزTo make your heartظآز

10:58.032 --> 11:01.104
ظآزWarm againظآز

11:04.304 --> 11:08.080
ظآزYou really don't need to chaseظآز

11:08.976 --> 11:11.504
ظآزNo need to chaseظآز

11:12.176 --> 11:15.696
ظآزThat quiet and steady happinessظآز

11:17.930 --> 11:18.971
Where are you going?

11:19.770 --> 11:21.131
To Jingzhao Prefecture.

11:21.570 --> 11:23.690
Doesn't work start at the Mao hour?

11:23.690 --> 11:24.890
It's still early.

11:25.491 --> 11:26.290
What's wrong?

11:28.371 --> 11:29.731
I want you to take a walk with me.

11:30.451 --> 11:31.251
A walk?

11:33.451 --> 11:34.690
But I'm a cripple.

11:35.491 --> 11:36.331
I'll push you.

11:39.410 --> 11:40.091
Alright.

11:47.290 --> 11:48.851
What did His Highness call himself?

11:49.011 --> 11:49.890
A cripple.

11:50.851 --> 11:52.176
Are you crazy? So loud.

11:52.176 --> 11:52.816
Come on.

11:53.570 --> 11:54.851
Didn't you ask me?

11:56.731 --> 12:00.091
I'm shocked. Her Highness is admirable.

12:05.890 --> 12:06.930
Send it to the Prefecture.

12:10.050 --> 12:10.851
Slow down.

12:12.290 --> 12:13.872
When my mom left the mountain,

12:14.770 --> 12:16.331
she was only 19.

12:16.810 --> 12:19.530
As soon as she entered the capital,
she met my father.

12:21.091 --> 12:21.890
At that time,

12:22.650 --> 12:25.611
the Ye family was just ordinary,
living outside the city outskirts.

12:26.290 --> 12:27.530
They were not rich,

12:28.211 --> 12:30.530
with an empty shell
of a scholarly family.

12:31.091 --> 12:33.251
My mom saw that my father was handsome,

12:33.491 --> 12:36.131
fell in love at first sight,
and wanted to marry him.

12:36.611 --> 12:38.331
Did your grandfather
agree to this match?

12:38.570 --> 12:39.650
Of course, he didn't.

12:40.810 --> 12:42.170
But he had no choice either.

12:42.491 --> 12:44.971
So, he simply let my mom have her way.

12:46.410 --> 12:49.851
Their marriage made a stir
in the capital back then.

12:50.810 --> 12:53.530
I heard the late emperor gave a mansion
to the Ye family

12:54.011 --> 12:56.410
along with a plaque
with an inscription, Family of Charity

12:56.810 --> 12:57.930
to be hung in their house.

12:59.011 --> 13:01.851
Red carpets lined the road,
and guards carried the bridal sedan.

13:02.091 --> 13:04.211
Eighty boxes of dowry,
full of gold and jewels.

13:04.770 --> 13:07.050
Even the accompanying maids
were dressed better

13:07.331 --> 13:09.371
than the ladies
from ordinary official families.

13:10.251 --> 13:12.371
You talk as if you saw it
with your own eyes.

13:12.731 --> 13:14.971
It was a grand wedding, known to all.

13:18.211 --> 13:21.971
My grandfather often said
my mom's life was too smooth.

13:22.530 --> 13:24.331
Even heaven couldn't stand it,

13:25.290 --> 13:27.570
so they made her suffer
by marrying my father.

13:28.371 --> 13:31.371
My grandmother disliked her;
my uncle was domineering,

13:32.050 --> 13:33.170
and my father was cowardly.

13:34.091 --> 13:36.530
At first, they were afraid of Lishan.

13:37.170 --> 13:39.410
My mom lived peacefully.

13:40.410 --> 13:44.371
But after Lishan Mountain was closed,
their attitudes changed.

13:45.371 --> 13:48.731
They became harsh,
even wanting to drive her to death.

13:49.770 --> 13:50.810
You told me about this.

13:51.211 --> 13:53.810
Your mom was seriously ill
and was cast out of the house.

13:54.371 --> 13:55.930
Later, she died at Zhengyi Temple.

13:57.690 --> 13:58.731
I lied to you.

14:03.930 --> 14:05.371
My mom's death was suspicious.

14:06.331 --> 14:07.851
I had always suspected it.

14:08.371 --> 14:10.480
I didn't know the truth
until the day of the banquet.

14:12.570 --> 14:14.170
My grandmother killed my mom.

14:17.290 --> 14:20.011
Back then,
when my mom was seriously ill,

14:21.170 --> 14:24.211
I found my father,
wanting him to see her one last time.

14:25.410 --> 14:26.971
This act enraged my grandmother.

14:27.650 --> 14:31.650
When I was away looking for a physician,
she murdered my mom.

14:35.371 --> 14:38.611
So that day,
you returned to Ye Mansion for revenge.

14:40.890 --> 14:42.570
They stole a very important item

14:43.131 --> 14:44.371
from my mom.

14:45.331 --> 14:46.570
I made a plan.

14:47.170 --> 14:49.451
(I hired someone
to pretend to be a wizard.)

14:50.050 --> 14:51.650
(I also found Ms. Wang's weakness)

14:52.131 --> 14:53.770
(and had her help me scare my father.)

14:57.290 --> 14:58.011
Go away.

14:58.011 --> 14:59.731
(My father felt guilty towards my mom,)

14:59.930 --> 15:02.410
so with just a little scare,
he lost his wits.

15:03.690 --> 15:05.091
Have you found the item now?

15:06.731 --> 15:07.690
I have some leads.

15:11.851 --> 15:13.091
Do you still hate them?

15:21.371 --> 15:22.170
Mo Xiuyao,

15:23.731 --> 15:27.491
do you think there will be a day
when the sun doesn't shine?

15:31.930 --> 15:34.930
The sun rises and sets
in an endless cycle.

15:36.050 --> 15:39.331
Tomorrow is a new day.

15:53.290 --> 15:54.851
My pinwheel spins faster than yours!

15:55.170 --> 15:55.851
Wait a moment.

15:57.810 --> 15:58.690
Stop blowing!

15:58.810 --> 15:59.890
You're cheating.

16:00.011 --> 16:00.930
I'm going to blow.

16:01.011 --> 16:01.890
Take a look.

16:02.050 --> 16:03.290
How much is this pinwheel?

16:03.290 --> 16:04.211
Three wen.

16:05.200 --> 16:06.131
Here.

16:09.136 --> 16:13.552
ظآزMy life is full of ups and downsظآز

16:15.312 --> 16:19.472
ظآزEvery wound shows traces of loveظآز

16:20.464 --> 16:25.520
ظآزI've seen all the withering plants
in this worldظآز

16:26.416 --> 16:29.104
ظآزUntil you went over the hillsظآز

16:29.552 --> 16:31.792
ظآزTo come close to meظآز

16:33.392 --> 16:37.584
ظآزI saw your tender yet unwavering eyesظآز

16:39.728 --> 16:43.952
ظآزQuietly full of joy and sorrowظآز

16:44.848 --> 16:50.576
ظآزWhen it's over, I stand in the lightظآز

16:50.992 --> 16:55.536
ظآزIn the reunion,
I comprehend the partingظآز

16:56.752 --> 17:01.968
ظآزWith half a lifetime of separation,
I send love to the distanceظآز

17:02.896 --> 17:08.944
ظآزAs I travel through wind and frost,
I gaze at your figureظآز

17:08.944 --> 17:14.256
ظآزYou never forget me,
and I always miss youظآز

17:19.211 --> 17:20.491
Your Highnesses.

17:21.530 --> 17:22.770
You've returned.

17:23.691 --> 17:24.491
I'm off.

17:25.411 --> 17:26.290
Going home?

17:27.810 --> 17:28.891
Send her home.

17:28.931 --> 17:29.731
No need.

17:30.640 --> 17:32.050
I want to walk by myself.

17:33.610 --> 17:35.451
Well then, see you tonight.

17:36.330 --> 17:37.130
See you tonight.

17:38.891 --> 17:39.691
Wait.

17:47.850 --> 17:49.731
Come and look.

17:49.731 --> 17:51.451
Five wen for a skewer!

17:51.451 --> 17:52.290
Want one?

17:53.971 --> 17:54.770
This one?

17:54.770 --> 17:55.610
Five wen.

17:55.610 --> 17:56.451
Want one?

18:03.600 --> 18:05.680
(Xiangqi Pavilion)

18:17.530 --> 18:19.850
Well? Did you find out the whereabouts
of the edict?

18:21.770 --> 18:23.290
Tell me. Who has it?

18:24.304 --> 18:25.610
The current Dowager Consort,

18:25.616 --> 18:26.610
Qin Zheng.

18:30.610 --> 18:33.130
(I thought it was Marquis Muyang
who pressured the Ye family.)

18:33.691 --> 18:36.610
(Turns out it was Qin Zheng
who took the edict.)

19:01.530 --> 19:02.451
You're awake.

19:04.090 --> 19:06.290
You shouldn't have come often.

19:06.480 --> 19:08.011
What if your father finds out?

19:08.976 --> 19:10.211
It doesn't matter.

19:10.736 --> 19:12.251
I just like you.

19:12.784 --> 19:14.290
And the Empress Dowager dotes on you.

19:16.330 --> 19:17.891
I know you well.

19:18.130 --> 19:19.770
So, what brings you here?

19:20.491 --> 19:21.290
Look at this.

19:22.090 --> 19:22.891
How did this happen?

19:23.691 --> 19:25.731
Calluses from riding
and archery practice.

19:27.610 --> 19:29.050
What does this have to do with me?

19:29.168 --> 19:30.896
I have nothing to do.

19:31.024 --> 19:33.211
Bored, so terribly bored.

19:33.680 --> 19:36.251
Qin Zheng, please help me
secure a position.

19:36.570 --> 19:38.050
With a job, I won't be bored.

19:38.211 --> 19:41.850
The Zhechong Prefecture wants men
good at archery and horsemanship.

19:42.011 --> 19:44.211
I've been training hard
and improved a lot.

19:44.290 --> 19:45.610
I'm qualified to work there.

19:45.936 --> 19:47.451
I can help you find a job,

19:47.971 --> 19:49.370
but not in the Zhechong Prefecture.

19:49.744 --> 19:52.112
Real fights happen there.

19:52.112 --> 19:55.570
If anything should happen to you,
how would I explain it to your father?

19:56.400 --> 19:58.211
Then why can Qin Cang do it?

20:00.496 --> 20:03.171
He has campaigned in Huaixi for years.

20:03.411 --> 20:04.290
Why compare?

20:05.931 --> 20:08.411
Anyway, you just have to help me.

20:11.312 --> 20:12.891
Qin Cang also just returned, right?

20:15.536 --> 20:17.691
You are both brothers.
Why must you compete with him?

20:18.251 --> 20:19.491
I'm not his brother.

20:19.660 --> 20:20.980
His surname is Qin. Mine is Zhou.

20:21.861 --> 20:23.700
You are both your father's sons,

20:24.021 --> 20:25.781
just with different surnames.

20:26.541 --> 20:29.460
Blood ties cannot be erased.

20:33.620 --> 20:35.301
Since you hold your father in awe,

20:36.021 --> 20:38.061
do you really not
acknowledge your brother?

20:44.900 --> 20:48.021
Fine! If you don't do it,
he won't do it either.

20:48.261 --> 20:49.101
Happy?

20:50.160 --> 20:51.541
Qin Zheng

20:52.741 --> 20:55.460
is sophisticated,
with a good background.

20:56.140 --> 20:57.541
She is also decisive and ruthless.

20:58.021 --> 20:58.980
One more thing,

20:59.861 --> 21:01.460
I don't know why

21:01.660 --> 21:04.940
she fully believed
the Empress Dowager was the chosen one.

21:05.261 --> 21:08.304
So, since she entered the palace,
she's been close to the Empress Dowager.

21:08.420 --> 21:11.021
And whatever the Empress Dowager did,
she gave her full support.

21:18.581 --> 21:20.061
Now I somewhat doubt

21:20.380 --> 21:22.900
if the edict is really in her hands.

21:24.140 --> 21:24.821
Why?

21:26.220 --> 21:28.460
That edict involves the Heiyun Cavalry

21:28.980 --> 21:30.460
and the Empress Dowager's reputation.

21:30.741 --> 21:33.541
Would she really keep such an item
in her possession?

21:34.980 --> 21:37.620
Whether against Lishan
or the former Prince Ding,

21:37.821 --> 21:40.021
it was Marquis Muyang who acted.

21:40.061 --> 21:42.061
He is the blade
in the Empress Dowager's hand.

21:42.448 --> 21:43.741
But why did Dowager Consort Qin

21:43.741 --> 21:46.220
take the edict
from Ye Mansion in the end?

21:46.781 --> 21:47.940
If she has ulterior motives,

21:48.380 --> 21:51.541
she will surely hold onto the edict.

22:02.021 --> 22:02.821
Guard Qin.

22:04.380 --> 22:05.180
Young Lord.

22:05.660 --> 22:06.501
Heading out?

22:08.101 --> 22:08.900
Yes.

22:10.940 --> 22:13.301
Did you just come back
from the Linjiao Courtyard?

22:14.061 --> 22:15.568
I chatted with the Dowager Consort.

22:16.061 --> 22:17.301
She gave me a fine horse.

22:17.460 --> 22:19.261
It's a good horse from Cangbei.

22:20.101 --> 22:22.220
However, I'm not fond
of riding and archery.

22:23.056 --> 22:25.200
But you're skilled
in riding and archery.

22:25.301 --> 22:27.821
How about I give the fine horse to you?

22:30.420 --> 22:31.220
No, but thanks.

22:34.480 --> 22:35.920
(Astrology)
(Astrological Divination)

22:43.341 --> 22:44.660
Are you interested in this?

22:46.640 --> 22:47.261
You know what?

22:47.261 --> 22:49.700
The Dowager Consort
has quite a deep understanding

22:49.700 --> 22:50.741
of astrology.

22:51.261 --> 22:53.900
She says all things in the world
have their own ways.

22:54.460 --> 22:57.101
Fathers and sons, brothers,
all have their own bonds.

22:57.980 --> 22:59.061
If you are interested,

22:59.301 --> 23:00.752
how about I take you

23:00.752 --> 23:02.261
to see the Dowager Consort next time?

23:04.900 --> 23:05.700
No need.

23:15.440 --> 23:18.704
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

23:23.341 --> 23:24.140
Prefect Mo.

23:25.460 --> 23:28.101
Someone has reported
that eight years ago, Ye Wending,

23:28.301 --> 23:30.861
along with his servant, Sun Fu,

23:31.301 --> 23:32.900
murdered a maidservant.

23:33.581 --> 23:35.700
The whereabouts of the remains
are unknown.

23:36.380 --> 23:38.821
Take some men to Ye Mansion
and arrest Sun Fu.

23:39.261 --> 23:40.460
Make him confess,

23:40.900 --> 23:42.620
and find out where the body was buried.

23:43.900 --> 23:45.821
Ye Mansion?

23:46.301 --> 23:47.660
Your wife's family home.

23:48.220 --> 23:49.900
Is there another Ye Mansion
in the capital?

23:52.460 --> 23:53.821
That maidservant's name was Yanlu.

23:54.380 --> 23:56.420
Her family lived
in Tulin Alley, East Ward.

23:56.861 --> 23:59.620
Her parents are still alive,
and she has a young brother.

24:00.460 --> 24:02.261
Back then, after Sun Fu killed her,

24:02.380 --> 24:04.220
he lied to her family,
saying Yanlu had gone

24:04.220 --> 24:05.840
to Lishan Mountain with her masters.

24:06.341 --> 24:07.460
Once you find her dead body,

24:07.660 --> 24:10.700
if verified,
send her body to her family.

24:11.700 --> 24:12.980
- Yes.
- Yes.

24:18.900 --> 24:20.301
What about the Penglai Alley case?

24:26.341 --> 24:27.341
Here it is.

24:27.861 --> 24:30.128
Everyone who participated that day

24:30.224 --> 24:31.536
is on this list.

24:37.220 --> 24:39.741
Your Highness, why do you want
to investigate these people?

24:42.261 --> 24:44.861
After we received the news,
we immediately mustered our troops.

24:45.261 --> 24:47.341
Jingzhao Prefecture and Penglai Alley

24:47.700 --> 24:49.101
are three wards apart.

24:50.021 --> 24:52.220
Once we reached Penglai Alley,
we split into two groups.

24:52.541 --> 24:54.101
Four entrances on the front and back.

24:54.180 --> 24:55.861
At most,
the third quarter of the Xu hour.

24:56.140 --> 24:57.501
Our plan was flawless.

24:58.220 --> 25:00.900
Our timing was very tight.

25:01.821 --> 25:03.620
But just as we were about
to capture Red Fox,

25:04.781 --> 25:06.700
someone rushed over and rescued him.

25:07.341 --> 25:10.261
So, you suspect someone among us
leaked the information?

25:13.460 --> 25:14.821
They ran into us.

25:15.180 --> 25:17.140
It means they must have
just received the message.

25:17.460 --> 25:18.460
So the leaker

25:20.061 --> 25:22.061
is among the guards we brought along.

25:22.861 --> 25:23.821
Go and investigate.

25:24.420 --> 25:27.700
Find out who wasn't at the scene
when we tried to capture Red Fox,

25:28.180 --> 25:30.541
or who left midway.

25:31.900 --> 25:34.460
I took a rough look at this list.

25:34.620 --> 25:36.900
They are all newcomers
without deep roots in the capital.

25:36.900 --> 25:38.101
If someone turned traitor,

25:38.180 --> 25:41.101
it's likely that they were bought off
with money.

25:42.620 --> 25:44.900
Then check their recent spending.

25:45.341 --> 25:48.700
Who has purchased property?
Who is in debt?

25:48.821 --> 25:49.821
Investigate it clearly.

25:50.180 --> 25:52.101
Since it is someone who can be bought,

25:52.980 --> 25:56.460
there must be a reason
they need the money.

25:58.380 --> 25:59.180
Yes.

26:06.980 --> 26:08.140
Your Highness, be careful.

26:08.420 --> 26:09.460
Don't burn yourself.

26:19.821 --> 26:21.900
Your Highness, let me do it.

26:22.140 --> 26:22.940
No.

26:41.301 --> 26:42.501
Your Highness, be careful.

26:43.261 --> 26:44.101
Your Highness.

26:51.741 --> 26:54.220
Any movement from Jingzhao Prefecture?

26:54.620 --> 26:56.336
They're investigating Yuan Fang's case.

26:56.460 --> 26:57.940
Although Red Fox gave himself away,

26:58.101 --> 26:59.501
I've sent him out of the city.

27:00.261 --> 27:01.861
This lead is now dead for them.

27:01.861 --> 27:03.101
You can be at ease for now.

27:03.861 --> 27:06.861
Are we just going
to watch them tread on us?

27:08.781 --> 27:10.821
Prince Ding is not our enemy.

27:12.620 --> 27:16.261
Mo Xiuwen died at the hands
of Zhou Jing and the Empress Dowager.

27:16.940 --> 27:20.261
Mo Xiuyao is bent on upending the case
of his brother and the Heiyun Cavalry.

27:22.261 --> 27:23.541
We can work with him.

27:25.741 --> 27:27.861
He's long since sided with the Emperor.

27:27.940 --> 27:29.140
What does that matter?

27:30.101 --> 27:32.101
His goal is to deal with Marquis Muyang.

27:33.061 --> 27:35.021
The Empress Dowager
trusts Marquis Muyang.

27:35.380 --> 27:36.861
The greater Mo Xiuyao's power grows,

27:36.861 --> 27:39.821
the more fiercely the Emperor will fight
with the Empress Dowager.

27:42.160 --> 27:43.821
The situation is complex and dynamic.

27:44.140 --> 27:46.420
Things may not go exactly as you wish.

27:52.061 --> 27:55.861
Your Highness,
you can see the situation.

27:56.101 --> 27:58.620
Why are you bent on treating Mo Xiuyao
as a mortal enemy?

28:06.261 --> 28:07.261
Who let you in?

28:08.501 --> 28:10.261
I just knocked on the door.

28:17.341 --> 28:18.301
You're injured.

28:19.700 --> 28:23.101
I'm injured.
I accidentally fell yesterday.

28:23.140 --> 28:25.261
His Highness was just
helping dress my wound.

28:27.140 --> 28:28.341
I shall take my leave.

28:43.460 --> 28:46.140
That day, I saw you go out.

28:51.380 --> 28:54.460
You must have been mistaken.

28:55.061 --> 28:58.101
That day, I was dead drunk
and sleeping the whole time.

28:59.420 --> 29:00.700
How could I have gone out?

29:24.061 --> 29:26.101
How does it feel? Does it hurt?

29:27.021 --> 29:27.821
It doesn't hurt.

29:41.420 --> 29:42.220
Give it a try.

29:45.781 --> 29:47.101
You are recovering very well.

29:47.581 --> 29:49.420
Standing up is just a matter of time.

29:49.541 --> 29:50.700
No need to be so surprised.

29:51.101 --> 29:53.900
I also need to see how your leg recovery
is progressing,

29:54.101 --> 29:56.420
so I can prepare the next prescription
for you.

30:20.432 --> 30:26.288
ظآزLove is not just romanceظآز

30:28.220 --> 30:31.101
If you can stand,
try taking a couple of steps forward.

30:31.408 --> 30:35.504
ظآزWhy do two struggling souls make a vowظآز

30:35.792 --> 30:38.160
ظآزAnd stake everythingظآز

30:40.176 --> 30:44.400
ظآزHardship makes us sensibleظآز

30:44.541 --> 30:46.501
Yes, just like that.

30:46.900 --> 30:47.700
Take your time.

30:50.736 --> 30:53.936
ظآزTo live once more for each otherظآز

30:54.800 --> 30:59.600
ظآزTo become a better version
of ourselvesظآز

31:00.464 --> 31:04.080
ظآزLove has never been just this.
Who knowsظآز

31:04.080 --> 31:06.448
ظآزNobody acknowledges your persistenceظآز

31:06.448 --> 31:08.816
ظآزIf the soul comes with thornsظآز

31:08.816 --> 31:12.016
ظآزEmbrace to feelظآز

31:12.656 --> 31:15.856
ظآزOr the green branch offered as a tutorظآز

31:15.856 --> 31:19.632
ظآزLike friends
always standing side by sideظآز

31:19.920 --> 31:23.568
ظآزLove is but a beginning,
knowing each other day and nightظآز

31:23.568 --> 31:29.904
ظآزOn such a long road,
holding hands and never letting goظآز

31:30.128 --> 31:33.680
ظآزOnly then do we understand why loveظآز

31:33.680 --> 31:38.320
ظآزMeans more than one thingظآز

31:41.061 --> 31:41.861
Your Highness.

32:08.061 --> 32:09.541
Are you feeling unwell?

32:26.460 --> 32:27.261
Your Highness.

32:31.021 --> 32:32.101
Are you alright?

32:45.700 --> 32:46.501
Li.

32:49.781 --> 32:50.660
Thank you.

32:53.456 --> 32:57.776
ظآزThe little and big things left
in each other's livesظآز

32:58.320 --> 33:02.544
ظآزAlong the way,
we've skipped the explanation of loveظآز

33:02.544 --> 33:05.072
ظآزSeeing a complete lifeظآز

33:05.072 --> 33:10.736
ظآزBecoming mirrors for each otherظآز

33:11.152 --> 33:14.864
ظآزLove has never been just this.
Who knowsظآز

33:14.864 --> 33:17.296
ظآزNobody acknowledges your persistenceظآز

33:17.296 --> 33:19.792
ظآزIf the soul comes with thornsظآز

33:19.792 --> 33:23.312
ظآزEmbrace to feelظآز

33:23.312 --> 33:26.768
ظآزOr the green branch offered as a tutorظآز

33:27.220 --> 33:29.700
Your leg problem has been neglected
for so many years.

33:30.061 --> 33:33.341
I mentioned it several times,
but you never let me try.

33:34.261 --> 33:36.861
I had no choice
but to push you a little.

33:38.460 --> 33:40.341
Thank you then.

33:44.021 --> 33:47.061
Yao, I never meant to harm you.

34:23.696 --> 34:25.072
(Pastries)

34:25.661 --> 34:26.980
So many pastries.

34:26.980 --> 34:28.100
So much money.

34:28.100 --> 34:29.221
So much food.

34:30.020 --> 34:31.420
Come on! Handing out money!

34:32.240 --> 34:33.181
Quick!

34:33.181 --> 34:33.940
Handing out money!

34:34.141 --> 34:34.861
Your Highness.

34:35.261 --> 34:36.240
What is going on here?

34:36.272 --> 34:38.020
They're giving out money.

34:39.940 --> 34:42.221
Attention, everyone!
His Highness is in a good mood

34:42.221 --> 34:43.261
and will reward you all.

34:43.261 --> 34:46.256
We're handing out snacks and money.

34:46.821 --> 34:47.580
It's all of ours!

34:47.580 --> 34:48.181
- It's all of ours!
- Come.

34:48.181 --> 34:48.980
- Catch!
- Come on.

34:48.980 --> 34:49.744
Catch!

34:49.744 --> 34:51.060
It's all of ours. Line up.

34:51.824 --> 34:52.701
It's mine.

34:52.701 --> 34:53.781
Give me one!

34:53.781 --> 34:54.621
I want one too!

35:01.900 --> 35:02.861
This is tonic soup.

35:03.341 --> 35:05.821
Starting today,
you no longer need to take medicine.

35:05.940 --> 35:08.900
Acupuncture will change from once a day
to once every other day,

35:09.141 --> 35:10.821
until you can walk normally.

35:13.940 --> 35:17.221
This process will only be longer
than mending the broken leg bone,

35:17.661 --> 35:19.580
and it must also not be taken lightly.

35:20.741 --> 35:24.221
Two bowls of tonic soup daily,
finished before the Xu hour.

35:24.580 --> 35:25.861
And you must eat more.

35:26.261 --> 35:27.980
After meals, you can walk moderately

35:28.221 --> 35:30.741
to help with healing
and restoring vitality.

35:37.020 --> 35:38.821
Thank you, Li.

35:40.781 --> 35:42.621
How many more times
are you going to thank me?

35:43.141 --> 35:44.701
I'm truly very grateful to you.

35:47.420 --> 35:49.261
I never thought I would stand again.

35:50.861 --> 35:52.261
You healed my leg,

35:53.301 --> 35:54.980
but I was once suspicious of you,

35:55.741 --> 35:57.301
thinking you had ulterior motives.

35:57.900 --> 35:59.100
And I lost my temper with you.

36:00.261 --> 36:02.221
I promised to go
to your family home with you,

36:03.980 --> 36:05.341
but I broke my promise.

36:08.940 --> 36:10.100
Now I finally realize

36:11.100 --> 36:14.221
you actually didn't believe
I could cure your leg before.

36:15.980 --> 36:17.341
Since you didn't trust me,

36:17.980 --> 36:20.221
why did you agree
to let me treat your leg?

36:21.741 --> 36:22.661
You are so persistent.

36:23.380 --> 36:24.621
Without letting you have a try,

36:24.940 --> 36:26.980
who knows what you might do?

36:28.080 --> 36:29.200
Like the whole bandit thing.

36:29.200 --> 36:30.544
ظآزSmooth out the creasesظآز

36:30.544 --> 36:34.320
ظآزSo we can tightly fit togetherظآز

36:34.320 --> 36:37.296
ظآزWithout you, there's no meظآز

36:37.424 --> 36:40.048
ظآزPassing by the worldظآز

36:40.048 --> 36:41.488
ظآزPart of my broken selfظآز

36:41.488 --> 36:43.728
ظآزFinds our places in an embraceظآز

36:43.728 --> 36:45.424
ظآزFulfilling our wishesظآز

36:45.584 --> 36:50.128
ظآزLovers remain calm and composedظآز

36:50.832 --> 36:52.912
ظآزLike you, like meظآز

36:53.168 --> 36:56.176
ظآزIt's like a fond dreamظآز

37:18.030 --> 37:18.830
Your Highness.

37:20.030 --> 37:22.030
I heard you've lost your appetite

37:22.149 --> 37:23.709
and not slept well at night.

37:24.269 --> 37:27.310
I've prepared a soup to help you sleep.
Please have some, Your Highness.

38:04.589 --> 38:06.629
Why haven't you gone to work,
Your Highness?

38:07.390 --> 38:08.350
Today is a day off.

38:10.430 --> 38:13.030
Why do I feel like
Your Highness is always on leave?

38:16.830 --> 38:18.870
Jingzhao Prefecture collects case files

38:19.350 --> 38:20.830
and handles matters, large and small.

38:21.430 --> 38:22.310
My staff and I

38:22.629 --> 38:25.189
often work late every night.

38:26.109 --> 38:27.269
You think I'm not busy,

38:27.709 --> 38:29.749
but that's only because other officials

38:30.069 --> 38:32.350
go to banquets after work,

38:32.669 --> 38:35.149
while I never attend banquets

38:35.390 --> 38:36.709
and go straight home instead.

38:39.589 --> 38:41.830
Well then, it seems I was wrong.

38:49.950 --> 38:50.749
By the way,

38:51.629 --> 38:54.589
regarding your mom's maidservant, Yanlu,

38:55.950 --> 38:58.910
we found her dead body
and sent her body to her family.

38:59.950 --> 39:02.549
This case is now being handled
by Jingzhao Prefecture.

39:04.109 --> 39:05.910
How will they sentence Mr. Fu
and Ye Wending?

39:06.910 --> 39:07.990
The murderer will be dead.

39:08.430 --> 39:10.229
The accomplice will be removed
from office.

39:16.709 --> 39:17.749
I don't work today.

39:18.229 --> 39:20.950
Is there anything you want to do?
I can do it with you.

39:22.950 --> 39:24.629
There's nothing I want to do.

39:25.189 --> 39:26.390
What about things you want?

39:27.149 --> 39:30.310
Just name it, and I'll find it for you.

39:31.549 --> 39:32.109
Really?

39:36.069 --> 39:37.589
There are many things I want.

39:38.069 --> 39:39.990
Delicious foods, beautiful things,

39:40.310 --> 39:41.189
fun things,

39:41.310 --> 39:42.350
jewelry,

39:42.390 --> 39:43.549
houses,

39:43.629 --> 39:44.629
and antiques.

39:46.069 --> 39:46.709
Okay, let's go.

39:47.269 --> 39:48.069
Where to?

39:49.269 --> 39:50.589
Jin, prepare the carriage.

39:50.950 --> 39:51.470
Yes.

39:55.408 --> 39:58.608
(Jinbao Shop)

40:02.870 --> 40:03.910
Why did we come here?

40:04.870 --> 40:05.830
To buy something.

40:06.790 --> 40:08.470
No, I'm not going.

40:10.589 --> 40:13.470
Jinbao Shop is a rival to my shop.

40:14.310 --> 40:17.709
Jinbao Shop is always full of customers.

40:17.709 --> 40:18.950
It's infuriating enough.

40:18.950 --> 40:20.510
You want to buy things from that shop?

40:23.990 --> 40:25.109
Let's go to Shubao Shop.

40:25.430 --> 40:26.229
No.

40:27.669 --> 40:29.910
It's owned by the same proprietor
as Jinbao Shop.

40:30.510 --> 40:33.470
So are Qibao Shop,
Huibao Shop, and Linbao Shop.

40:34.910 --> 40:36.589
So, we can't go to any of these shops?

40:39.549 --> 40:43.350
If we rule those out,
only Shende Shop is left.

40:43.910 --> 40:45.669
I can't just take you to the Shende Shop

40:45.990 --> 40:48.589
and buy something for you
in your own shop.

40:49.069 --> 40:51.069
In any case, I can't benefit my rival.

40:51.408 --> 40:53.030
They won't earn a single coin from me.

40:55.669 --> 40:56.830
I'll pay, anyway.

40:57.950 --> 40:59.069
Pick whatever you like.

41:04.149 --> 41:04.749
Alright then.

41:14.390 --> 41:15.749
What would you like to buy?

41:16.430 --> 41:19.229
We here mainly deal in gold,
silver, jade, precious stones,

41:19.589 --> 41:21.510
porcelain, and ritual items.

41:22.510 --> 41:26.269
Over here is the celadon
we just received this morning.

41:26.269 --> 41:28.390
Is there anything you like?

41:29.510 --> 41:30.870
Not that impressive.

41:31.109 --> 41:32.470
Is there anything better?

41:34.350 --> 41:35.709
Is this your first visit?

41:36.030 --> 41:38.669
You might not know,
but our shop has a rule.

41:39.549 --> 41:43.109
Well, to see the better goods,
one must buy 10,000 qian worth of goods.

41:44.629 --> 41:47.510
But I want to see them now. Can't I?

41:48.149 --> 41:48.990
Well...

41:54.189 --> 41:55.109
Please wait a moment.

42:04.510 --> 42:07.669
Are you two here
to see our shop's celadon?

42:08.870 --> 42:11.069
Could you please rest
in the private room for a while?

42:11.470 --> 42:13.669
I'll have our staff
make some preparations

42:14.069 --> 42:17.510
and show you our finest celadon pieces.

42:18.189 --> 42:19.990
Aren't your shop's rules very strict?

42:20.830 --> 42:23.910
I heard new customers must
spend 10,000 qian to see better goods.

42:24.149 --> 42:26.310
This is my first time here,
and I'm still allowed?

42:27.790 --> 42:30.149
Rules are not fixed here.

42:30.549 --> 42:32.350
Your presence here is a great honor

42:32.629 --> 42:33.990
for our shop.

42:34.430 --> 42:35.790
Rules don't matter then.

42:36.990 --> 42:37.709
This way, please.

42:40.400 --> 42:42.992
(Preview)

42:43.990 --> 42:44.830
On January twelfth,

42:45.149 --> 42:46.419
(Lishan Academy)
Ye Li left the mountain alone

42:46.419 --> 42:47.510
(Lishan Academy)
with an imperial decree.

42:48.189 --> 42:49.510
(She left the mountain alone)

42:49.990 --> 42:51.430
(for the capital.)

42:52.069 --> 42:53.390
Why can't Qingshuang do it?

42:54.629 --> 42:55.430
Qingshuang?

42:57.069 --> 42:58.430
What do you say, Qingshuang?

42:59.910 --> 43:01.549
So, Her Highness is mentally sick?

43:02.709 --> 43:04.350
You want to overturn their case?

43:04.912 --> 43:05.936
Wait for the right time,

43:06.608 --> 43:08.030
and heaven will help us.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
ظآزBoth joy and grief
make the trip worthwhileظآز

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
ظآزTrying to catch up
to your own lost shadowظآز

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
ظآزWithin the wilds, echoes thriveظآز

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
ظآزClear mind leads to a clear pathظآز

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
ظآزBe grateful to your lossesظآز

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
ظآزMake your steps weightlessظآز

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
ظآزPut every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through timeظآز

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
ظآزMake headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your paceظآز

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
ظآزUnbound by formظآز

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
ظآزUnbound by formظآز
